README for ADXL35 interruptions test app
Author/Contact: Antonio Linan <alinan@zolertia.com>

Description:

This application test the Accelerometer interruptions in the following
manner:

 * Single tap: toggle led red
 * Double tap: toggle green led
 * Free fall: toggle blue led

The ADXL345 sensor is a temperature sensor and its already integrated as
part of the Zolertia Z1 mote.

Tools:

None

Known bugs/limitations:

None.
